  "text": "### 3.3 Dormancy  \nIf your account has:\n- No activity (deposits or withdrawals) for 12 months, AND\n- No customer contact for 12 months  \nYour account becomes \"dormant.\" We will:\n1. Send letter to last known address\n2. Mark account as dormant (no impact on you)\n3. Continue accruing interest\n4. Maintain full access (deposit/withdrawal possible)  \n---",
